query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(mc mi t ak) */ select min(mi.info) AS release_date,
min(t.title) AS modern_internet_movie
from title AS t
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on t.id = mc.movie_id AND t.production_year < 2010
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.note like '%internet%' AND mi.info IS NOT NULL AND ( mi.info like 'USA:% 199%' OR mi.info like 'USA:% 200%')
inner join aka_title AS ak
on t.id = ak.movie_id
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on t.id = mk.movie_id;
